            <title>小红书充斥假证有网红更到廉署打卡，或涉及伪造证件及冒充廉政公署人员</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/09/06/little-red-book-girl-pictures-in-hkicac-crime-of-forgery/hottopic/spotlight/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=little-red-book-girl-pictures-in-hkicac-crime-of-forgery</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/09/06/little-red-book-girl-pictures-in-hkicac-crime-of-forgery/hottopic/spotlight/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Ngan Ivan]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 10:00:36 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[城中热话]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[社交网络]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[ICAC]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1261157</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">近日一名自称为「时尚博主」和模特儿的刘姓女子，分享她来港旅游时的打卡照并上传到小红书，而其中一张在廉政公署门外的打卡照却引起争议。这名女网红在照片中一身黑色西装的打扮，打卡时出示「首席调查主任」委任证，被指伪造证件及冒充廉政公署人员。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1261178 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/2024090560141-454x580.jpg" alt="" width="454" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/2024090560141-454x580.jpg 454w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/2024090560141.jpg 705w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 454px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1261180" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/2024090560306-498x580.jpg" alt="" width="498" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/2024090560306-498x580.jpg 498w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/2024090560306.jpg 773w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 498px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：抖音</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1261164 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/458304253_1589645195-326x580.jpg" alt="" width="326" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/458304253_1589645195-326x580.jpg 326w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/458304253_1589645195.jpg 506w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 326px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">图片来源：<a href="https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2021470/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E5%A5%B3%E7%B6%B2%E7%B4%85%E5%87%BA%E7%A4%BAICAC-%E5%A7%94%E4%BB%BB%E8%AD%89-%E5%BB%89%E7%BD%B2%E5%A4%96%E6%89%93%E5%8D%A1-%E5%B0%8F%E7%B4%85%E6%9B%B8-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E7%A8%B1%E5%8F%AF%E7%A7%81%E8%A8%8A%E7%99%BC%E6%A8%A1%E7%89%88-%E5%BB%89%E7%BD%B2-%E5%86%92%E5%85%85%E5%BB%89%E7%BD%B2%E4%BA%BA%E5%93%A1%E5%8D%B3%E5%B1%AC%E7%8A%AF%E7%BD%AA?fbclid=IwY2xjawFGUzNleHRuA2FlbQIxMAABHZR3bvJqopV2_FtOlyPTW6QUr8xctmwGyWdZbpFlTKvzbLE5yw48nAqM8w_aem_4Y3o8JLACKPv-Cd2oBbshw">星岛</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">女网红在北角廉政公署总部大楼门外打卡，帖文更写上「ICAC 查案！不方便透露！这里是 TVB 迷来香港必去的吧！」。她一身西装的打扮，又向网友展示印有她姓名的「廉政公署执行处授权证」，当中印有其「首席调查主任」的职级、证件号码和证件有效期。她事后被网民指控伪造证件及冒充廉政公署人员，目前女子已经将小红书上的所有帖文删除。有关事件曝光后，有网民发现小红书上原来充斥着大量类似的伪造证件情况，不少游客到廉署打卡时都会出示自己伪造的 ICAC 证件，亦有人会为自己喜爱的艺人伪造证件，包括古天乐、陈奕迅和一众韩星，更有人表示可以提供模版供他人制作相关的 ICAC 证件。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1261166 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img20240904wa0040red-423x580.jpg" alt="" width="423" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img20240904wa0040red-423x580.jpg 423w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img20240904wa0040red.jpg 656w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 423px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1261165 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img20240904wa0037red-478x580.jpg" alt="" width="478" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img20240904wa0037red-478x580.jpg 478w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img20240904wa0037red.jpg 738w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 478px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">图片来源：<a href="https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2021470/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E5%A5%B3%E7%B6%B2%E7%B4%85%E5%87%BA%E7%A4%BAICAC-%E5%A7%94%E4%BB%BB%E8%AD%89-%E5%BB%89%E7%BD%B2%E5%A4%96%E6%89%93%E5%8D%A1-%E5%B0%8F%E7%B4%85%E6%9B%B8-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E7%A8%B1%E5%8F%AF%E7%A7%81%E8%A8%8A%E7%99%BC%E6%A8%A1%E7%89%88-%E5%BB%89%E7%BD%B2-%E5%86%92%E5%85%85%E5%BB%89%E7%BD%B2%E4%BA%BA%E5%93%A1%E5%8D%B3%E5%B1%AC%E7%8A%AF%E7%BD%AA?fbclid=IwY2xjawFGUzNleHRuA2FlbQIxMAABHZR3bvJqopV2_FtOlyPTW6QUr8xctmwGyWdZbpFlTKvzbLE5yw48nAqM8w_aem_4Y3o8JLACKPv-Cd2oBbshw">星岛</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">廉政公署就事件作出回应，引用《廉政公署条例》第 13C 条，指冒充廉署人员即属犯罪 ，一经定罪最高可被判处监禁一年及罚款 25,000 元。网民对事件的反应各有不同，有人认为女子行为属于违法亦有人认为女子只是 Cosplay 不属违法，有人就表示不理解到廉政公署打卡的行为。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">资料及图片来源：<a href="https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2021470/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E5%A5%B3%E7%B6%B2%E7%B4%85%E5%87%BA%E7%A4%BAICAC-%E5%A7%94%E4%BB%BB%E8%AD%89-%E5%BB%89%E7%BD%B2%E5%A4%96%E6%89%93%E5%8D%A1-%E5%B0%8F%E7%B4%85%E6%9B%B8-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E7%A8%B1%E5%8F%AF%E7%A7%81%E8%A8%8A%E7%99%BC%E6%A8%A1%E7%89%88-%E5%BB%89%E7%BD%B2-%E5%86%92%E5%85%85%E5%BB%89%E7%BD%B2%E4%BA%BA%E5%93%A1%E5%8D%B3%E5%B1%AC%E7%8A%AF%E7%BD%AA?fbclid=IwY2xjawFGUzNleHRuA2FlbQIxMAABHZR3bvJqopV2_FtOlyPTW6QUr8xctmwGyWdZbpFlTKvzbLE5yw48nAqM8w_aem_4Y3o8JLACKPv-Cd2oBbshw">星岛</a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/06/little-red-book-girl-pictures-in-hkicac-crime-of-forgery/hottopic/spotlight/">小红书充斥假证有网红更到廉署打卡，或涉及伪造证件及冒充廉政公署人员</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
